msgctxt "#32151"
msgid "Automatic Pillow install is not available on this Kodi platform/Python version.\n\nInstall Pillow manually into the add-on site-packages folder or use a Kodi build that includes Pillow."
msgstr "Automatische Pillow-installatie is niet beschikbaar op dit Kodi-platform/Python-versie.\n\nInstalleer Pillow handmatig in de add-on site-packages-map of gebruik een Kodi-build die Pillow bevat."

